citation.excerpt: Implementation of algorithm presented in OpenAI's publication "Multi-Agent Actor-Critic for Mixed Cooperative-Competitive Environments" (Lowe et al., https://arxiv.org/pdf/1706.02275.pdf)

description.excerpt: Does not include "Inferring policies of other agents" and "policy ensembles"
Implementation of Multi-Agent Reinforcement Learning algorithm(s). Currently includes: MADDPG

installation.excerpt:
multiagent-particle-environment: follow install instructions in https://github.com/openai/multiagent-particle-envs 
Tested on Spread environment.
